description:
When we first connected with so many people on Twitter, we had no idea what a GM was. All people from any part of the world, connected through the NFT world, echo these words like a mantra that keeps repeating to get their luck.
Sometime later, we realized that GM stands for “Good Morn- ing.” We don’t know where the trend is coming from, it could be that we just wanted to make things feel more concise, or it was a ploy to have fewer characters typed. But we know these abbreviations, mostly interpreted positively by people.
Perhaps, it has developed into a mandatory culture for people swimming in the NFT world.
We try to respond to this by creating a collective work contain- ing several photo stories and packaging into a digital zine, re- leased into two volumes.
Let’s dive into the sea of meanings about GM itself from vari- ous perspectives, mindsets, and creative freedom. Enjoy!

